erms of revenue, but the cost of that revenue was waking up every day and c=
learing out a support inbox. Yes, we could have hired to solve for this, bu=
t then=C2=A0 I&#39;d have to manage other people (something I&#39;m not int=
erested in). It reminds me of <a href=3D"https://ofone.co/how-to-build-a-bu=
siness-you-accidentally-hate/" style=3D"color:#f9415d!important;font-weight=
:600!important;text-decoration:underline;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMac=
SystemFont,San Francisco,Helvetica Neue,Helvetica,Ubuntu,Roboto,Noto,Segoe =
